Package com.example.courseanalyzer.analyzer.studyplananalyzer.model

Class Module

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.courseanalyzer.analyzer.studyplananalyzer.model.Module
  • public class Module
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the module of the curriculum which consists of courses. Module can be mandatory or optional.

    Due to the curriculum a student has to achieve a minimum of 6 ECTs of courses of an optional module and has to collect a minimum 12 ECTs of optional modules.

    A module is default true
